{"tid":2152794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政界響應爆買洗版","createTime":"2020-08-12T07:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T07:43:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21d25c5bd879df8002f5abd77e14f1a1c7588579","tid":2152794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/ESTWHUGL3U3IVND2R4MNYAHURQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FESTWHUGL3U3IVND2R4MNYAHURQ%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=79d49b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FESTWHUGL3U3IVND2R4MNYAHURQ%2F&h=767f1288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/ESTWHUGL3U3IVND2R4MNYAHURQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n政界響應爆買洗版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5kMEtopGGg4nt-miC2NISny2MR8=/911x787/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P2FEDTEU4RHMUJLP2VQ5GJNTAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5kMEtopGGg4nt-miC2NISny2MR8%3D%2F911x787%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP2FEDTEU4RHMUJLP2VQ5GJNTAM.gif&h=4e9acc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仇栩欣<br />\n<br />\n政界人士、KOL昨紛紛響應網上號召爆買《蘋果》，並呼籲港人要買到斷市。有區議員一口氣購入100份供街坊取閱。他們在社交媒體上載與《蘋果日報》的合照，加上標籤#SupportAppleDaily、#WeNeedAppleDaily。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨陳淑莊昨凌晨在fb上載所購買的《蘋果》，呼籲「香港人同蘋果一定撐落去！」黨友譚文豪同樣在凌晨上載，更展示四份，並留言稱：「一家四口一人一份，好合理。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zlOGVzRAk0SLt5DO3sNqCHCwS8Y=/476x439/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3ZV3IMVKMIA5T76MOEHGJWJHI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzlOGVzRAk0SLt5DO3sNqCHCwS8Y%3D%2F476x439%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3ZV3IMVKMIA5T76MOEHGJWJHI.gif&h=a80c3597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q_-J_u_NWQ98xhQiANSK71DOub0=/476x439/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4TGCQJ2HWTK6N4CMPSCOPQ4DKY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq_-J_u_NWQ98xhQiANSK71DOub0%3D%2F476x439%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4TGCQJ2HWTK6N4CMPSCOPQ4DKY.gif&h=94f2309c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁凱晴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仇栩欣上庭不忘買報<br />\n<br />\n職工盟秘書長李卓人在fb上載與《蘋果》合照，寫上「中共出動200警力去執行國。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學化學博士鄺士山（K Kwong）在fb呼籲「全香港今（昨）日做一件事。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大批網民在留言區上載響應「爆買」的《蘋果》照片，甚至有人買。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員盧俊宇和深水埗區議員甄啟榮亦買100份《蘋果》供街坊取閱，獲。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東區區議員仇栩欣昨需上庭審訊，但亦不忘支持《蘋果》，上載一張她。。。。。。。。。"}]}